ander who?"],[4754,4888,"Alexander Miller..."],[4992,5155,"That's Alexander Miller?"],[5163,5280,"Ms. Miller's son?"]],"43":[[12,66,"Shit."],[129,241,"That's Alexander Miller?"],[304,533,"He's even dreamier in person."],[621,658,"Sir,"],[688,859,"that woman is... is delusional."],[900,1046,"She claims she's your mother."],[1071,1209,"The CEO of Phoenix Group."],[1247,1280,"Sir,"],[1326,1484,"it's my son's wedding today."],[1539,1655,"We would be honored"],[1655,1789,"if you could attend the reception"],[1835,1989,"after you meet with"],[1989,2102,"the real Ms. Miller."],[2147,2306,"It's an honor to meet you, sir."],[2356,2485,"I'm Sean's girlfriend,"],[2506,2598,"the mayor's daughter,"],[2656,2769,"but you can call me Brittany."],[2811,2994,"If you need anything in this town,"],[2994,3153,"my family's at your service."],[3415,3453,"Brittany,"],[3495,3549,"shut up."],[3611,3649,"What?"],[3670,3791,"It's not every day you meet"],[3799,3953,"the Alexander Miller."],[4062,4166,"Also think about it."],[4216,4350,"If Ms. Miller comes to"],[4354,4504,"my brother's wedding party too,"],[4529,4646,"we'll be the talk of the town."],[4733,4854,"If you want to invite my mother"],[4854,4925,"to your party,"],[4984,5130,"why don't you ask her yourself?"],[5142,5321,"Oh, what a brilliant idea."],[5363,5451,"If you would be so kind"],[5451,5559,"as to lead us to her?"],[5622,5701,"There's no need for that."],[5814,6097,"My mother is here right now."],[6544,6585,"Where..."],[6639,6710,"Where is she?"]],"44":[[66,100,"Sir,"],[229,279,"are you playing"],[287,400,"some kind of trick on us?"],[467,596,"I don't see Ms. Miller anywhere."],[642,813,"I would certainly recognize her"],[813,917,"if she was in my town."],[925,1055,"Well, of course you would."],[1088,1192,"Nothing happens here"],[1192,1347,"without the mayor knowing about it."],[1426,1514,"Are you suggesting"],[1514,1689,"I wouldn't recognize my own mother?"],[1960,2164,"If, if what you're saying is true,"],[2227,2364,"when did she come to our town?"],[2385,2481,"Fifteen years ago."],[2573,2665,"My mother came here"],[2665,2773,"to live in seclusion,"],[2806,2940,"after she stepped down"],[2940,3086,"as the Phoenix CEO."],[3257,3403,"Fifteen years ago?"],[3407,3528,"That's not possible..."],[4287,4433,"I'm so sorry I took so long, Mother."],[4733,4796,"Come here,"],[4825,4888,"my son."],[5005,5155,"You've gotten so old."],[5367,5447,"I missed you."],[5655,5797,"You're a beautiful man now."],[6673,6802,"Phoenix Group's CEO?"],[6852,6940,"Impossible..."]],"45":[[41,196,"She's really Ms. Miller?"],[246,383,"Phoenix Group's CEO?"],[496,654,"There has to be some mistake."],[688,892,"She's nothing but a filthy woman"],[896,1067,"who works for the orphanage."],[1117,1251,"That beggar could not possibly"],[1259,1363,"be the real Ms. Miller."],[1747,1818,"Ms. Miller,"],[1910,2089,"please excuse my girlfriend's"],[2143,2302,"disgraceful behavior."],[2381,2519,"I take full responsibility."],[2598,2702,"Punish me as you see fit."],[2756,2873,"Our adoptive mother"],[2873,2994,"is the famous Ms. Miller?"],[3440,3541,"What have we done?"],[3816,3887,"One moment, Mother."],[4045,4112,"Are you Grace?"],[4387,4462,"Take care of Mother."],[4696,4775,"Let me handle this."],[5121,5209,"Now, it's time for you all"],[5209,5317,"to explain yourselves."]],"46":[[4,175,"This, this is all a misunderstanding."],[638,763,"Apologize to my mother."],[796,829,"Now!"],[1222,1272,"Ms. Miller,"],[1305,1376,"I beg of you."],[1413,1480,"I'm sorry."],[1530,1651,"I'm so, so sorry."],[1705,1856,"You're only apologizing now"],[1856,1976,"because you know who I am."],[2031,2114,"As I said,"],[2252,2398,"you would regret being born."],[2469,2523,"Guards,"],[2577,2669,"get him out of my sight."],[2698,2831,"Make sure I never see his face"],[2831,2957,"in this city again."],[3332,3357,"Sean,"],[3365,3516,"if that's the real Ms. Miller,"],[3520,3607,"then who did you invite"],[3607,3712,"to my birthday dinner?"],[3845,3887,"Tell her."],[3933,4062,"Tell her she's never really met me."],[4120,4316,"Tell her that I'm the real CEO"],[4316,4400,"of Phoenix Group."]],"47":[[246,362,"You thought you actually deserved"],[362,475,"to see the real Ms. Miller?"],[500,596,"It was just some employee"],[596,725,"that I paid to pretend."],[759,942,"I didn't think you'd be stupid enough"],[959,1051,"to not notice."],[1063,1101,"And now"],[1117,1238,"look at the trouble you've caused."],[1626,1680,"Ms. Miller,"],[1735,1897,"this worthless girl has caused nothing"],[1897,1960,"but trouble."],[1993,2085,"I'll kill her myself"],[2106,2185,"if you'll forgive me."],[2231,2502,"Someone like you doesn't even deserve"],[2502,2635,"to work at the Phoenix Group."],[2723,2806,"Remove him."],[3294,3349,"Ms. Miller,"],[3591,3657,"we were wrong."],[3753,3853,"We'll never do anything"],[3853,3941,"like this again."],[4012,4049,"Please,"],[4095,4162,"have mercy..."],[4266,4446,"forgive us just this once."],[4504,4813,"You all tortured people for years."],[4888,5025,"If I was to forgive you,"],[5088,5246,"you would go on and continue"],[5246,5409,"to hurt innocent people."],[5442,5518,"Take them away."],[5538,5643,"Deal with them accordingly."],[5793,5860,"Take them away."],[5914,5993,"Wait, wait, wait."],[6018,6072,"No, I..."],[6197,6231,"No."],[6810,6915,"Where do you think you're going?"],[6986,7123,"I am not done with you two."]],"48":[[29,116,"What are you planning on doing"],[116,179,"with these two?"],[283,479,"You two wanted this house so badly?"],[567,646,"Burn it down."],[742,838,"You don't deserve it."],[850,930,"You heard my mother."],[992,1042,"Burn it down."],[1059,1096,"Now!"],[1113,1167,"Yes, sir."],[4020,4062,"Mother."],[4183,4262,"Mother, please."],[4350,4450,"We're your children."]],"49":[[0,166,"All these years in seclusion,"],[221,346,"I gave you everything."],[400,504,"And yet all you wanted"],[504,621,"was for me to die?"],[679,917,"You've really shown your true colors."],[996,1067,"And you know what?"],[1126,1255,"Now you never have to"],[1255,1359,"call me mother again."],[2014,2085,"And you."],[2143,2252,"You're not off the hook."],[2306,2410,"I'll deal with you later."],[2677,2752,"Yes, Ms. Miller."],[3269,3324,"My dear,"],[3370,3511,"somebody very special"],[3511,3636,"I want to introduce you to."],[3687,3762,"Grace."],[3837,3983,"This is my son, Alexander."],[4037,4204,"It's an honor to meet you, sir."],[4254,4304,"Please,"],[4362,4441,"you're my sister now."],[4512,4642,"There's no need for formalities."],[4683,4721,"Mother,"],[4754,4796,"I've arranged"],[4796,4904,"a welcome banquet for you"],[4904,5021,"at the Cloud Peak Restaurant."],[5159,5305,"What better occasion"],[5422,5563,"to introduce my daughter"],[5563,5672,"to the whole world."],[5730,5997,"The future heiress of the Phoenix Group."]],"50":[[12,129,"It's a historical day"],[133,225,"for the Phoenix Group."],[250,625,"The city must know our CEO is back."],[671,829,"I'll send out the invitations."],[1514,1647,"Is that your boyfriend?"],[1672,1826,"The one that was studying abroad?"],[1885,1922,"Yes."],[1997,2097,"He promised me"],[2106,2189,"when he came back home"],[2189,2352,"that he would propose to me."],[2481,2590,"I'm expecting him"],[2590,2740,"to pop the question any time now."],[2827,2961,"That's wonderful."],[3019,3069,"Take the call."],[3078,3182,"But why don't you also invite him"],[3182,3274,"to the banquet tonight,"],[3274,3319,"okay?"],[3386,3424,"Okay."],[3770,3803,"Hi."],[3983,4091,"Cloud Peak Restaurant?"],[4116,4137,"Yeah,"],[4137,4212,"I can meet you there."],[4546,4771,"There's, um, actually something important"],[4771,4854,"I need to tell you."]],"51":[[2248,2473,"Who's that beautiful young woman?"],[2498,2548,"She must be"],[2548,2652,"someone important to be"],[2656,2806,"at Phoenix Group's banquet tonight."],[3324,3382,"Nathan."],[4141,4212,"Victoria?"],[4308,4450,"Long time no see, bestie."],[4896,5130,"What, what's going on here?"],[5184,5305,"What does it look like?"],[5492,5647,"Your best friend and I are together now."],[5943,5976,"But..."]],"52":[[20,137,"But you promised me"],[137,216,"you'd give me a ring"],[225,300,"when you came back."],[337,437,"Oh, he did get a ring."],[588,754,"Just not for you, loser."],[1038,1205,"Shocked to see our son engaged"],[1205,1334,"to someone worthy of him?"],[1388,1655,"A proper match at last."],[1714,1843,"Unlike you."],[1851,2039,"And your useless, poor mother"],[2064,2206,"who can't possibly help him"],[2206,2289,"in his career."],[2339,2394,"That's right."],[2448,2581,"My mother's a secretary"],[2581,2660,"at Phoenix Group,"],[2686,2769,"and she got Nathan"],[2773,2882,"the regional manager position"],[2882,2944,"at the company."],[3065,3157,"Things change"],[3157,3324,"when you have the right connections."],[3415,3507,"Isn't that right, sweetie?"],[3757,3853,"So that's why you chose"],[3853,3962,"my best friend over me?"],[4062,4208,"How could you both do this to me?"],[4283,4404,"Shut your mouth."],[4738,4825,"Oh honey,"],[4896,5034,"save yourself the humiliation"],[5034,5121,"and leave."],[5230,5376,"You don't belong here."]],"53":[[196,262,"Everything's set."],[312,433,"The city's most powerful elite"],[433,533,"are here to meet Grace."],[2002,2185,"Grace deserves this moment."],[2231,2323,"After tonight,"],[2323,2427,"everyone will know"],[2427,2544,"that she's the heiress"],[2552,2652,"of the Phoenix Group."],[3315,3378,"Wait, what?"],[3445,3624,"Someone's causing trouble to my sister?"],[3920,4033,"Did you honestly think"],[4033,4187,"you could compete with me?"],[4245,4325,"You're just the daughter"],[4325,4504,"of some poor, crazy woman"],[4517,4654,"who can't even walk."],[4875,4963,"And that dress..."],[5038,5100,"what did you do,"],[5138,5205,"steal it?"],[5251,5380,"Trash like you could never afford"],[5380,5476,"a dress like that."],[5584,5680,"Probably borrowed it"],[5680,5839,"to pretend she's not poor."],[5918,5997,"Just like her mother,"],[5997,6143,"pretending to be someone she's not."],[6231,6289,"Let me return it"],[6297,6448,"to whatever store you stole it from."],[7240,7273,"Mom?"],[8274,8375,"Don't worry, sweetheart."],[8558,8654,"Your mother will always"],[8654,8779,"protect you now, okay?"]],"54":[[33,158,"How dare you throw wine"],[158,300,"on my future daughter-in-law."],[354,487,"How disgusting."],[529,696,"This is why poor people like her"],[696,905,"have no business at events like this."],[905,1038,"And who might you be?"],[1080,1192,"I'm Nathan's father,"],[1263,1347,"Bill Carter."],[1384,1526,"And I am his mother,"],[1551,1593,"Helen."],[1601,1935,"So, your son is the young man"],[1935,2156,"that my daughter was interested in?"],[2206,2389,"Just as I suspect."],[2489,2660,"He's not worthy of my daughter."],[2786,2902,"Who are you to talk down"],[2902,3019,"to my son like that?"],[3036,3232,"Our son is the perfect match"],[3232,3370,"any girl could hope for."],[3457,3620,"Oh, really?"],[4633,4717,"The three heirs"],[4717,4846,"of the largest corporations?"],[4963,5105,"Only Phoenix Group is above them."],[5142,5242,"What are they doing here?"]],"55":[[37,129,"I'm James Bryant"],[129,291,"from the Sterling International Group."],[333,500,"It's an honor to meet you, Grace."],[575,625,"Grace,"],[667,763,"would you be honored to meet me"],[771,905,"at the dinner for sometimes?"],[967,1134,"I would love to take a travel with you"],[1142,1184,"when you can."],[1238,1376,"My schedule is completely open."],[1455,1530,"I, I..."],[1555,1605,"Sweetheart,"],[1718,1801,"don't be afraid."],[1906,2106,"You really do deserve someone better."],[2260,2298,"Grace,"],[2302,2435,"these are some of the finest young men"],[2435,2485,"in the city."],[2565,2723,"And if none of them are to your desire,"],[2806,2907,"there are CEOs,"],[2907,3023,"there are entrepreneurs,"],[3040,3132,"and there are architects"],[3144,3219,"eager to meet you."],[3370,3461,"What's going on?"],[3520,3624,"Why are all these rich men"],[3624,3791,"surrounding trash like you,"],[3807,3966,"you pathetic whore?"],[3999,4108,"Since when do you know people"],[4108,4191,"with real money?"],[4283,4575,"You manipulative little slut."],[4596,4754,"What other secrets are you hiding?"],[5017,5084,"You think you're good enough"],[5084,5184,"to touch my sister?"],[5547,5626,"Did you just say"],[5747,5818,"sister?"]],"56":[[29,175,"I thought you said she was an orphan?"],[358,596,"How could she be Alexander's sister?"],[742,821,"Alexander,"],[867,946,"surely there's been"],[955,1096,"some sort of mistake."],[1126,1297,"And who exactly do you think you are"],[1305,1372,"to question me?"],[1584,1659,"Alexander,"],[1714,1843,"you must be confused."],[1881,1943,"Grace is nothing"],[1943,2118,"but a worthless orphan."],[2306,2394,"It's true."],[2394,2548,"She's nothing but trash."],[2827,2927,"She's garbage!"],[2948,3069,"Nothing but garbage!"],[3741,3778,"Who..."],[3887,4058,"who are you?"]],"57":[[29,145,"Since you're so desperate"],[145,346,"to find out who my daughter is,"],[404,604,"you, you'll find out soon enough."],[771,829,"And you."],[905,1067,"You will see exactly"],[1067,1180,"what you threw away."],[1363,1468,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[1526,1693,"please welcome the CEO"],[1705,1814,"of Phoenix Group,"],[1868,1989,"Ms. Miller."]],"58":[[337,383,"She"],[412,542,"she, she, she can't be."],[563,704,"Is that really"],[804,980,"The CEO of the - The CEO of the"],[980,1088,"Phoenix Group? - Phoenix Group?"],[1247,1309,"Thank you."],[1526,1785,"Thank you all for coming this evening."],[1835,1956,"During my absence,"],[1956,2173,"I worked the hardest,"],[2218,2385,"most low-paying jobs."],[2394,2569,"I wanted to understand"],[2590,2769,"the struggle of the less fortunate"],[2769,2927,"and what I ended up finding"],[2965,3123,"was something unexpected."],[3211,3536,"I found a daughter with a heart of gold."],[3566,3770,"Tonight, I'm proud to introduce"],[3803,4091,"the future heiress of the Phoenix Group."],[4225,4341,"You worthless bitch."],[4354,4462,"This is all your fault!"],[4562,4758,"You made me betray Grace."],[4879,4975,"Don't blame me"],[4975,5046,"because you threw away"],[5046,5150,"someone important."],[5401,5522,"Grace, please,"],[5576,5672,"I never cared about her."],[5672,5772,"I've always loved you."],[5868,5980,"Just give me another chance."],[5980,6156,"I'll prove myself worthy."],[6368,6452,"Alexander."],[6969,7248,"Your sister is both kind and wise."],[7273,7357,"You need to trust"],[7365,7482,"that she'll do the right thing."]],"59":[[12,66,"Grace,"],[87,229,"Victoria deceived us all."],[304,492,"Our son truly cares for you."],[521,638,"Give him one more chance."],[671,767,"Yes, Grace."],[792,971,"You and Nathan have history."],[996,1163,"If you become our daughter-in-law,"],[1201,1368,"we'll treat you like our own."],[1397,1459,"When you thought"],[1459,1605,"my mom and I were nothing,"],[1680,1818,"you treated us like dirt."],[1935,2160,"And then you stood by and watched"],[2160,2281,"while Nathan betrayed me,"],[2314,2448,"and humiliated my mother."],[2473,2510,"Grace,"],[2523,2602,"I was wrong."],[2640,2790,"And even my parents see it now."],[2890,3111,"It'll never, ever happen again."],[3136,3207,"I swear."],[3249,3328,"You're only sorry"],[3336,3432,"because of who I am now."],[3549,3591,"Yes,"],[3636,3799,"I once had feelings for you."],[3908,3987,"But that's over."],[4166,4354,"I never want to see you again."],[4921,5046,"You think you're above me now?"],[5221,5547,"Pay me one hundred million dollars,"],[5547,5743,"or else everyone finds out"],[5743,5830,"how you really became"],[5830,5947,"the Phoenix Group heiress."],[6064,6156,"By sleeping with"],[6156,6373,"your own adoptive brother."]],"60":[[25,116,"How dare you."],[166,246,"That's a lie."],[354,462,"Truth doesn't matter."],[508,663,"My mother is a PR manager"],[663,746,"at Phoenix Group."],[771,992,"She can forge all the proof we need."],[1001,1121,"The press will eat it up."],[1163,1384,"And I'll back every word of it